  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "パラソルヘンべえは、SASサカタが開発し、エポックが発売したアクションゲームで、1990年に日本でリリースされました。",
      "lang": "ja",
      "source": "romu"
    },
    {
      "text": "Parasol Henbē (Japanese: パラソルヘンべえ, Hepburn: Parasoru Henbē) is a Japanese multimedia franchise created by Fujiko Fujio A (the pen name for Motoo Abiko). A manga series was published in Kodansha's Hero Magazine from the October 1989 to the January 1991 issues, with its chapters collected in two tankōbon volumes. A 200-episode anime television series, produced by Studio C&D, was broadcast on NHK from October 2, 1989, to January 12, 1991.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "wikipedia_en"
    }
